### 新增 Profile
#/manager/profileBO/add
POST http://{{dc3-manager}}/manager/profileBO/add
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

{
  "name": "测试模板",
  "share": false,
  "driverId": -1,
  "description": "测试模板"
}


### 更新 Profile
#/manager/profileBO/update
POST http://{{dc3-manager}}/manager/profileBO/update
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "测试模板",
  "share": false,
  "driverId": -1,
  "description": "测试模板"
}


### 根据 ID 查询 Profile
#/manager/profileBO/id/:id
GET http://{{dc3-manager}}/manager/profileBO/id/-1
Accept: */*
Cache-Control: no-cache



### 分页查询 Profile
#/manager/profileBO/List，支持name模糊查询，share\driverId精准查询
POST http://{{dc3-manager}}/manager/profileBO/List
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

{
  "name": "",
  "page": {
    "current": 1,
    "orders": [
      {
        "column": "id",
        "asc": false
      }
    ]
  }
}


### 根据 ID 删除 Profile
#/manager/profileBO/delete/:id
POST http://{{dc3-manager}}/manager/profileBO/delete/1
Accept: */*
Content-Type: application/json
Cache-Control: no-cache

